1
00:00:03,950 --> 00:00:07,820
Not only did you lose my daughter's journal...
你不仅弄丢了我女儿的日志

2
00:00:08,710 --> 00:00:11,874
but your polar bear blew up my village.
你的北极熊还炸毁了我的村子

3
00:00:11,942 --> 00:00:13,200
No.
不

4
00:00:13,314 --> 00:00:14,434
We don't know that.
谁说是我干的

5
00:00:15,710 --> 00:00:18,660
And your gorilla beat up my tiger.
而且你的大猩猩痛扁了我的老虎

6
00:00:19,970 --> 00:00:21,348
No good.
这可不好

7
00:00:25,220 --> 00:00:26,970
- Let's go. - No, no. Stay.
-我们走  -不  站住

8
00:00:27,028 --> 00:00:29,340
No, no, no, no, no.
不不  不行

9
00:00:31,940 --> 00:00:33,257
Yeah.
很棒

10
00:00:38,650 --> 00:00:39,828
Irony...
讽刺的是

11
00:00:40,700 --> 00:00:44,660
is me wanting to kill you
我全身上下每一个细胞

12
00:00:44,731 --> 00:00:47,400
with every fiber of my being...
都想要杀死你

13
00:00:50,370 --> 00:00:54,910
but loving my daughter more.
但我更爱我的女儿

14
00:01:04,700 --> 00:01:06,502
I miss her, too.
我也想念她

15
00:01:09,480 --> 00:01:11,340
She would have wanted you to...
她会想要你

16
00:01:12,370 --> 00:01:13,880
to keep going.
继续前行

17
00:01:22,034 --> 00:01:23,060
So!
所以

18
00:01:26,800 --> 00:01:27,860
Get going...
赶紧滚

19
00:01:28,740 --> 00:01:31,490
before I stop feeling sentimental.
在我恢复理智之前

20
00:01:35,160 --> 00:01:37,050
She's saying we don't have a ship.
她在说我们没有船

21
00:01:38,490 --> 00:01:40,320
Well, uh...
这样的话

22
00:01:40,930 --> 00:01:43,540
I have the perfect vessel for you.
我有艘船正适合你

